defaultOur Expertise and Achievements: defaultSince 1990 we have provided support and services to anyone whose human rights were violated
default as a result of conflict. Our interventions have reflected our range of expertise, from the right to a fair trial to the government’s positive obligation to protect life. We have a long record of working closely with NGOs and government authorities to shar
defaulte that expertise. And we have received wide recognition, as the first winner of the Parliamentary Assembly of the Council of Europe’s Human Rights Prize in 2009 alongside other honours.
defaultOur Judicial Review Experience: defaultWe have substantial experience as a th
